{"tid":2381900,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"一路射向外太空！日本飛機杯TENGA與火箭公司共同計畫邁向宇宙 發射獨一無二「飛機杯火箭」！","createTime":"2021-01-27T02:25:56.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-27T03:14:50.000Z","uid":28114,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8d727043a825beb743511015eb23a9e38673777b","tid":2381900,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T02:25:56.000Z","msg":"日本飛機杯大廠TENGA繼推出多款令紳士們意想不到的新奇產品後，今日他們決定將與日本知名火箭公司Interstellar Technologies首度合作，計劃打算將飛機杯打造成史上最狂、最獨一無二的「TENGA火箭」，並且「射進」外太空！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.toy-people.com/member/161167182943.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.toy-people.com%2Fmember%2F161167182943.jpg&h=89289fe4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n事實上早在先前，玩具人本站就已經搶先為各位電電小夥伴們介紹「宇宙TENGA機器人 DX火箭任務套組」，來因應這一次的火箭計劃。<br />\n<br />\n據官方網站所是出的資訊與情報圖指出，這枚TENGA火箭不僅將漆上經典的「標誌紅」以外，更在火箭外表上大大地寫著「愛與自由」，藉此來向全世界傳達「這是一個充滿愛與自由的世界」，不僅可以自由地去愛人，更自由地與你的伴侶享受生活！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.toy-people.com/member/161167183645.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.toy-people.com%2Fmember%2F161167183645.jpg&h=7fc2122e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n除此之外，TENGA火箭也將裝滿多達1000個人的願望，將大家的想法、想說的話、想達成的夢想都通通裝進這個紅色的「TENGA訊息艙」之中，並且與身穿太空裝的機器人「Tenga Robo」一同隨行，將願望通通傳送至太空中。<br />\n<br />\n而火箭內也還有一個是「數據偵測」的TENGA飛機杯，來做為偵測外太空變化的一個工具，當然由於現階段都還是處於亞軌道開發階段，因此實際上並不會停留在宇宙中太久，很快就會返回到地球上。"},{"pid":"229d235376c01f0afa4504ca5521e06408e43058","tid":2381900,"uid":28114,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T02:26:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.toy-people.com/member/161167191496.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.toy-people.com%2Fmember%2F161167191496.jpg&h=c73ed709&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.toy-people.com/member/161167193670.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.toy-people.com%2Fmember%2F161167193670.png&h=e89764fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nTENGA創辦人松本光一表示，事實上TENGA&times;Interstellar Technologies所合作的「TENGA ROCKET計畫」，最大的幕後功臣在於從事太空科技，同時也是名太空發展推動者的堀江貴文先生。<br />\n<br />\n推動此企劃的最大目的，在於希望能夠將「性」、「愛」這樣相當日常化的事情更加地平易近人，就如同火箭外所傳達的「愛與自由」一樣，特別是至今依然有不少人對於「性」觀念較為保守，那希望透過這樣的活動，來促使它更加「親民」，畢竟所謂的「性」就跟吃飯一樣，是生活中的一部分。<br />\n<br />\nTENGA&times;Interstellar Technologies的飛機杯火箭，預計將在2021年夏季發射出去，更多消息也請鎖定官方的最新情報。<br />\n<br />\n新聞來源： <a href=\"http://rocket.tenga.co.jp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Frocket.tenga.co.jp&d=TIKlq4bXcOIiQck3m%2BQSv732HZRMtn4xjJY4gFhUisg%3D&h=3844f69d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">rocket.tenga.co.jp</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.toy-people.com/?p=59247&amp;\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.toy-people.com%2F%3Fp%3D59247%26&d=TIKlq4bXcOIiQck3m%2BQSv732HZRMtn4xjJY4gFhUisg%3D&h=79e546a3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.toy-people.com/?p=59247&amp;</a>"},{"pid":"98166f34f5785de60c4b193b18fb2bcbd8130d76","tid":2381900,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T02:27:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/tenga_pr/status/1354082922979069955?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ftenga_pr%2Fstatus%2F1354082922979069955%3Fs%3D21&d=TIKlq4bXcOIiQck3m%2BQSv732HZRMtn4xjJY4gFhUisg%3D&h=7e973a60\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ftenga_pr%2Fstatus%2F1354082922979069955%3Fs%3D21&h=5d2f3dee\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/tenga_pr/status/1354082922979069955?s=21</a>"},{"pid":"b52082acd1ee949dca67db12cbd594cd9a7086f1","tid":2381900,"uid":35930,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T02:28:38.000Z","msg":"射上moon都唔益你"},{"pid":"2dfeff353c5555a045136d9b7f5997a034ee6e14","tid":2381900,"uid":69231,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T02:30:16.000Z","msg":"射到上太空<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c45d8202d4691bd09358417b1d9d1130e27a525c","tid":2381900,"uid":331590,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T02:40:16.000Z","msg":"畢竟所謂的「性」就跟吃飯一樣，是生活中的一部分。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n靠飛機杯滿足性生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f55f061c3c7372b3692cf6138af9bce631de842a","tid":2381900,"uid":310446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T03:14:50.000Z","msg":"今日四月一號？"}]}